@startuml
title UC14 - Notifications Sequence
actor "Registered User" as User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Notification API" as API
participant "Notification Service" as Svc
participant "Scoring Service" as Score
database "DB" as DB

== System creates (from UC06 scoring) ==
Score -> Svc : notifyMatchResult(matchId)
Svc -> DB : load participants + is_winner
Svc -> DB : insert MATCH_WON / MATCH_LOST (is_read = false)

== User views ==
User -> UI : Open notification bell
UI -> API : GET /notifications
API -> Svc : list(userId)
Svc -> DB : query notifications (newest first)
API --> UI : notifications + unread count
UI --> User : Show list + badge

== Mark read ==
User -> UI : Open a notification
UI -> API : PATCH /notifications/{id}/read
API -> Svc : markRead(id, userId)
Svc -> DB : set is_read = true
API --> UI : 200 OK
@enduml
